      type: "poem",
      title: "Diego and the Star Map of the Ancient Temple",
      description: "A young Mayan boy discovers a celestial map in an ancient temple that reveals the connection between earthly friendships and the vast cosmos above.",
      cover: "/covers/gen-e77b10c51e8f.svg",
      character: {"name": "Diego", "identity": "A curious young explorer who uncovers cosmic secrets in ancient ruins", "special": "He sees how friendships mirror the glowing constellations in hidden temple maps", "personality_tags": ["Curious", "Dreamy"]},
      addedAt: "2026-02-16",
      text: "In the jungle green where temples rise,\nLived Diego with his curious eyes,\nHe loved to climb the pyramid stone,\nBut often felt he walked alone.\n\nOne starlit night he found a door,\nHidden deep in temple floor,\nInside, the walls began to glow,\nWith constellations high and low.\n\nThe ancient map showed Venus bright,\nAnd Jupiter's majestic light,\nEach planet danced in painted gold,\nWith stories that the Maya told.\n\nAs Diego traced each starry line,\nHe saw how all the stars align,\nLike friends who come from far and near,\nTo make the night sky bright and clear.\n\nHe learned that just like stars above,\nWe're connected through our love,\nEach friendship is a shining light,\nThat guides us through the darkest night.\n\nNow Diego knows he's not alone,\nThe stars and friends have always shown,\nThat in this cosmic, vast embrace,\nWe each have found our special place.",
      target_age: 10,
      duration: 2,
      like_count: 55,
      save_count: 17,
      view_count: 257,
      categories: ["Space", "Friendship", "Ancient Civilizations", "Self-Discovery"],
