      description: "A baby dragon discovers a hidden friendship in a futuristic volcanic island, where glowing vines and robotic fireflies light the way to wonder.",
      cover: "/covers/gen-caa3a14bb706.svg",
      character: {"name": "Ember", "identity": "A lonely little dragon who finds warmth in unexpected friendship", "special": "His curiosity lights up hidden wonders in a world of glowing vines and robotic friends", "personality_tags": ["Curious", "Gentle"]},
      addedAt: "2026-02-21",
      text: "[RHYTHMIC]Beneath the sky of liquid gold,\nwhere neon rivers softly roll,\nEmber stirs on lava stone,\nhis scales like embers, warm, alone.\n\n[GENTLE]The island hums a lullaby,\na song of gears and wind so high,\nhe tilts his head—what’s that soft sound?\nA humming friend on shifting ground.\n\n[CALM]A silver fox with circuits bright,\nsteps from shadows into light,\n\"I’m Nova,\" chirps the fox so wise,\n\"I tend the vines that touch the skies.\"\n\n[JOYFUL]They dance where fireflies glow and play,\nthrough gardens lit in blues and gray,\nEmber learns each plant’s sweet name,\nand friendship burns like solar flame.\n\n[WHISPERING]Now side by side at twilight’s glow,\nthey watch the stars in patterns flow,\n\"The world is vast,\" the fox imparts,\n\"but home is where the heart finds art.\"\n\n[SLEEPY]Ember sighs, his eyelids close,\nas Nova’s tail wraps ‘round his toes,\nthe island breathes, the night is deep,\nand dreams take flight on wings of sleep.",
