      type: "song",
      title: "Stripe and the Whispering Bamboo",
      description: "A prehistoric tiger cub discovers his true self beneath the rustling bamboo grove, learning that his stripes are not just marks—but the map of his journey.",
      cover: "/covers/gen-e47bcd61e515.svg",
      character: {"name": "Stripe", "identity": "A curious tiger cub discovering his true path and purpose", "special": "His stripes hold the hidden map of his journey and destiny", "personality_tags": ["Curious", "Determined"]},
      addedAt: "2026-02-25",
      text: "[SINGING] Beneath the golden, setting sun,\nThe bamboo sways—a whispered tune,\nStripe the cub with amber eyes,\nWonders why the wind still sighs.\n\n[GENTLE] Are my stripes too bold, too bright?\nDo they hide me in the night?\nOr are they threads of stories old,\nWoven deep in earth’s embrace so cold?\n\n[HUMMING] Hmm-hmm-hmm, the leaves hum low,\nHmm-hmm-hmm, the river knows.\n\n[JOYFUL] Oh, little cub, don’t fear the light,\nYour stripes are stars that guide the night!\nThey dance with fireflies in flight,\nAnd paint the sky with dreams so bright!\n\n[PAUSE]\n\n[SINGING] One evening, as the crickets play,\nStripe met Owl on moonlit spray.\n\"Why do you hide?\" the wise one said,\n\"Your stripes are roots where courage’s fed.\"\n\n[GENTLE] The river hums a lullaby,\nOf ancient tales beneath the sky.\nOf cubs who learned to stand so tall,\nNot despite their stripes—but all.\n\n[HUMMING] Hmm-hmm-hmm, the earth sings deep,\nHmm-hmm-hmm, the secrets keep.\n\n[JOYFUL] Oh, little cub, don’t fear the dark,\nYour stripes are embers, glowing spark!\nThey light the path where dreams embark,\nAnd lead you home through meadows’ arc!\n\n[PAUSE]\n\n[SLEEPY] Now Stripe curls ‘neath bamboo’s grace,\nHis stripes no longer just a trace.\nBut maps of love, of time, of place,\nA cub who found his truest face.\n\n[GENTLE] So close your eyes, let dreams take flight,\nThe bamboo sings you through the night.\nFor every stripe, for every hue,\nIs proof that you are brave—and true.\n\n[HUMMING] Hmm-hmm-hmm, the stars align,\nHmm-hmm-hmm, the world is kind.",
