      text: "Chhat ke upar aasmaan mein, ek chhota sa mulaayam badal tha jiska naam tha Nimbus. Nimbus ka kaam duniya ka sabse khaas kaam tha \u2014 taaron se meethe sapne ikaththa karna aur sote hue bacchon pe chidakna.\n\nAaj raat taare khoob chamak rahe the. Nimbus ne apne narm haathon se ek sapna pakda \u2014 udne waale ghode ka, ek aur candy ke baag ka, aur ek pyaare dragon ka jo garam jhappi dena chahta tha.\n\nJab Nimbus tumhare ghar ke upar se guzra, usne apna phulphula badan hilaya, aur sapne chhoti chhoti barf ki phuhar ki tarah neeche aaye. Wo tumhare takkiye pe aaram se baith gaye, tumhara aankhein band karne ka intezaar kar rahe the.\n\n\"Meethe sapne dekho, chhote,\" Nimbus ne dheere se kaha, aur chaandni ki lakeer chhodta hua aage nikal gaya.",
