      title: "Chaand ki Lori",
      description: "Chaand apni meethi lori se sabhi jaanwaron ko sulata hai.",
      character: {"name": "Chaand", "identity": "The gentle night singer who lulls all creatures to sleep", "special": "Whispers sweet lullabies that make the whole world drift into dreams", "personality_tags": ["Gentle", "Warm"]},
      cover: COVERS.moonLullaby,
      addedAt: "2026-01-26",
      text: "Jab suraj pahaadiyon ke peeche chala gaya, Chaand dheere-dheere uthha aur Willow Meadow pe chandi ki roshni bikher di.\n\n\"Chup ho ja, chhoti lomdi,\" Chaand ne gaaya, aur lomdi apni khoh mein simat gayi.\n\n\"So ja, chhote ullu,\" Chaand ne gungunaya, aur ullu ne apna sar apne pankh ke neeche chhupa liya.\n\nPhir Chaand ne tumhari taraf dekha aur sabse meetha sur gaaya: \"Shubh raatri, mere chhote sapne dekhne waale. Subah tak taare tumhara khayal rakhenge.\"\n\nAur bas phir, poori duniya sukoon se so gayi.",
